  "steps": [
    {
      "explanation": "We will use the ideal gas law in microscopic form to find the number of molecules.",
      "notations": "P V = N k₍B₎ T"
    },
    {
      "explanation": "Define the given values from the problem.",
      "notations": "P = 1.0 × 10⁻¹² N/m², T = 0°C = 273 K, V = 1 cm³ = 1.0 × 10⁻⁶ m³, k₍B₎ = 1.38 × 10⁻²³ J/K"
    },
    {
      "explanation": "Solve the ideal gas law for N, the number of molecules.",
      "notations": "N = P V / (k₍B₎ T)"
